SUMMARY:2026 Women’s Success Summit - SHIFT: The CEO Advantage
DESCRIPTION:Does your business feel like it’s in constant reaction mode – always dealing with urgent fixes and putting out fires instead of leading with strategy? In today’s rapidly evolving marketplace\, reactive leadership won’t create sustainable growth. \nSHIFT: The CEO Advantage is a transformational experience designed for women business owners ready to step fully into their CEO role. This high-impact summit goes beyond inspiration\, offering practical strategies\, clear action steps\, and powerful mindset shifts to help you move from constant reaction to confident\, strategic leadership. You’ll surround yourself with 120 serious women business owners and walk away with meaningful connections. \nLed by renowned entrepreneur and eWomenNetwork Founder & CEO Sandra Yancey\, you’ll leave with renewed clarity\, momentum\, and an actionable plan you can implement immediately. \nSeats are limited. Reserve yours today.
