SUMMARY:What Does a Career With AI Look Like for You?
DESCRIPTION:In this virtual panel\, Microsoft professionals in software engineering\, AI product management\, marketing\, and human resources will share their career journeys\, the skills that matter\, and how AI impacts their work. Moderated by a Microsoft Software Engineer\, this discussion will offer practical insights and advice for students exploring careers in technology. \nThe session will begin with a brief welcome and introduction from The Mentoring Project and North Seattle Tech Talks. Then our guest panelists will take over\, giving their introductions and covering the main topics. We’ll wrap up with a brief\, moderated Q&A.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/what-does-a-career-with-ai-look-like-for-you/
