DESCRIPTION:​Where capital\, innovation\, and leadership converge. \n​Overview: Get ready to connect\, invest\, and discover what’s next. The Seattle Investor Summit + Showcase returns in 2026\, convening leading venture capitalists\, corporate innovators\, and high-growth startups from across the Pacific Northwest and beyond. \n​This one-day event is designed to \n​Create meaningful connections between startups and potential investors and/or customers. \n​Showcase the breadth of Washington’s startup ecosystem (AI\, Cloud\, Space\, Defense\, Ag\, and more) \n​Help investors tap into the exceptional opportunities offered by Washington to build and scale a company \n​ What to Expect: \n​✔ Strategic Startup Showcases\n✔ Top VCs + Corporate Investors\n✔ Emerging Innovation Across Key Sectors\n✔ Networking\, Panels\, and 1:1 Meeting Opportunities \n​Agenda\n8:00 AM – Check-in table opens\, lite breakfast ready\n9:00 AM – Keynote\n10:00 AM – Networking break\n10:30 AM – Pitch tracks: The Autonomy Era\, The Rewiring\n12:00 PM – Networking lunch\n1:15 PM – Panel with Tim Porter (Madrona) and other local VCs\n2:00 PM – Keynote – Jaime Teevan\, Chief Scientist\, Microsoft\n2:45 PM – Networking break\n3:15 PM – Pitch tracks: The Rewiring\, The New Stack\n4:30 PM – Reception\, Hosted by Orrick\n6:30 PM – End \n​Don’t miss your chance to be part of this high-value summit at the intersection of innovation and investment.
